Subject: [PATCH] Fixes following managarm patch

---
 config.sub                                  |  8 +++++-
 gcc/config.gcc                              | 27 ++++++++++++++++---
 gcc/config/i386/i386-toast.h                | 10 +++++++
 gcc/config/i386/t-toast64                   |  3 +++
 gcc/config/toast-system.h                   |  2 ++
 gcc/config/toast.h                          | 29 +++++++--------------
